lead_paragraph: Fifth-seeded Romanian Simona Halep overcame a crisis of confidence in the second set to reach the final of the Rogers Cup with a 6-0 3-6 6-2 upset victory over second seed Angelique Kerber of Germany in Montreal on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Halep Upsets Kerber, Will Face Keys in Final
headline.main: Halep Upsets Kerber, Will Face Keys in Final
